Speaker 2: But you don't receive any refill, or you don't get billed

Speaker 2: And the doctor consultation is preserved.

Speaker 1: They pause you, I think, up to half a year,

Speaker 2: and you can get it once or twice a year maybe.

Speaker 1: You see what I'm saying?

Speaker 2: Yeah, so keep the prescription you said,

Speaker 1: just call and get it filled every once in a while?

Speaker 2: Yes, yes. So I pause it for them.

Speaker 1: Because you're not required to get it as often.

Speaker 2: You're not even required to get 25.

Speaker 1: You can get more, you can get less, you can get 10 pills once or twice a year

Speaker 2: to keep your account active and keep the same price.

Speaker 1: But you don't have to get it as often.

Speaker 2: Okay, yeah, that'll work out.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 1: Yeah, all right.

Speaker 1: All right.
